  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0da9\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The killer from the power line grabs the child",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that an 11-year-old child was electrocuted while playing in a relative's house in Wellawaya Kotaweheragala area.",
        "A child named RM Nuvan Netsara, who studied in 06th year of Malwattawala Vidyalaya, has died.",
        "The deceased child was playing in a relative's house and the child got tangled in an electric wire that was installed near a nearby broom."
      ],
